A surreal minimalist, ultra-realistic surreal composition featuring a perfectly spherical transparent liquid water orb floating weightlessly precisely in the center of the frame against a dark background, some stars in upper half far background, creating cosmic vibe.

Inside the orb exists a fully contained light-blue sky environment.

The entire interior is filled with open light-blue sky with a couple of faint white clouds in distance, subtly distorted by the curvature of the a turquoise oceanic water surface. vast, uninterrupted atmospheric space that enhances minimalism and scale.

Centered perfectly within the orb is a large dolphin suspended mid-leap, angled slightly upward as if gliding through air. The dolphin’s body forms a graceful arc, with its head pointing toward the upper-right quadrant while the tail curves gently downward toward the lower-left. Its fins are extended naturally, conveying motion yet frozen in a serene, weightless moment. The dolphin is the sole subject inside the sphere.

A soft golden rim light outlines the dolphin’s upper contour, tracing along the dorsal fin, snout, and tail edge, creating subtle separation from the lilac sky. Gentle atmospheric haze adds depth, especially toward the far interior edges of the sphere. The lighting remains cinematic yet delicate, preserving the minimalist mood.

The water orb itself is entirely liquid — with smooth organic curvature and realistic refraction. The internal sky and dolphin subtly distort near the edges of the sphere due to water optics. A faint horizontal waterline lightly bisects the orb, and small suspended air bubbles are visible in the lower portion, reinforcing the liquid nature. Soft highlights appear along the upper-left curve of the sphere, with no harsh reflections.

The overall atmosphere is serene, surreal, and elegant — minimalist yet cinematic, with breathtaking negative space and a single powerful subject contained within a self-sustained floating world.
